Interface IInboundEventSource<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ILifecycleComponent, ITenantLifecycleComponent

    public interface IInboundEventSource<T>
extends ITenantLifecycleComponent
    Entity that receives events from one or more IInboundEventReceiver, decodes them, and forwards them for processing.
